        <p class="text-lg opacity-90 leading-relaxed">Every minute spent fixing a broken cell in your free spreadsheet is profit leaking out of your business. If your estimating process is manual, you aren't building a business; you're maintaining a file. Real builders need a system, not a calculator.</p>
        <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-8">
          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg shadow-lg px-8">Compare Spreadsheet Costs vs Custom Software</button>
        </div>
      </div>
