    <p>
      Standard software often forces you to change your workflow to fit the tool. Custom software does the opposite.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">Custom Workflows for Custom Homes</h3>
    <p>
      Every builder has a "secret sauce" for how they estimate and manage. Your software should reflect your specific logic for waste factors, labor rates, and subcontractor management.
    </p>


